; R# 487 : Magic Shop
NUMBER 487
NAME Magic Shop
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This small room contains shelves of various magical implements and scrolls.
A small board lists the prices for the currently available goods.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 341
; Price Board
ITEM 0 1127
; Ucantsee
ITEM 9 693
;
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 0
Prices ar in gold crowns and all sales are final:
       
    Amulet of Thought      280           Scroll of Armor          130
    Pendant of Protection  200           Scroll of Confusion       80
    Pin of Wizardry        280           Scroll of Firestorm      250
    Ring of Strength       180           Scroll of Healing        100
    Rod of Lightning       240           Scroll of Identify       120
    Talisman of Vitality   280           Scroll of Protection     200
    Wand of Light          120           Scroll of the Elements    80
            
Simply state what you wish to purchase and it will be brought forth.
*DESCRIPTION_END
