;
; R# 2505 : Small Bedroom
NUMBER 2505
NAME Small Bedroom
ASTRAL
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The walls of this room are painted a pale orange in color. On one side
of a fireplace is an oak desk, while on the other is a matching oak bed. 
A tapestry hangs on one wall next to a window that looks out upon the
city. The frills and stuffed kitten upon the bed combine to give you a
feeling that this is a young woman's room.
*DESCRIPTION_END
; Door
ITEM 0 65 ADJ1=355 VAL1=200 VAL2=2503 VAL3=2505
; Fireplace
