EXTEND 3 covered with yellow sheets and a burgandy quilt with a starburst pattern on it.
; Tapestry
ITEM 4 250
; Window
ITEM 5 249
; Ucantsee
ITEM 9 693
;
IFPREVERB LOOK 2
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You see a candle holder with three candles in it and a silver flower in a small crystal vase on the desk.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 3
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You see a pillow and a small stuffed animal on the bed.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PULL 3
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You lift the stuffed kitten off the bed and give it a hug before putting it back.
  ECHO OTHERS %N picks up the stuffed kitten and hugs it before putting it back on the bed.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 4
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You see a beautiful tapestry. It has the image of a yellow-orange phoenix with bright yellow wing tips sitting on its nest in front of a red-ornage sunset.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 5
  CLEARVERB
  SHOWROOM 206
ENDIF
;
; R# 489 : Central Shaft, Third Floor
NUMBER 489
NAME Central Shaft, Third Floor
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
A crystal pillar rises from the floor up into the center of the tower, 
surrounded by the floating blocks of a spiral staircase. A few hushed
voices can be heard from the north, chanting can be heard from the east,
a noxious stench wafts in from the west, and what looks to be a meeting
room is to the south. A door marked "Office of the Loremaster" is to the
northwest.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 492
EXIT E 493
EXIT W 491
EXIT S 342
EXIT U 2506
EXIT D 2503
ITEM 0 65 VAL1=50 VAL2=490 VAL3=1201
; crystal pillar
ITEM 4 1700 ADJ1=77
EXTEND 4 which is the center of a floating spiral staircase
; Ucantsee
ITEM 9 693
;
; R# 490 : Office of Knowledge
NUMBER 490
NAME Office of Knowledge
ASTRAL
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
You stand in a scholarly office dominated by a wall-sized teak 
bookcase filled with tomes and librams. A white oak desk seems 
to be guarded by a wrymwood figure and covered to overflowing 
with all manner of documents, books and a single potted plant.  
