glow. A pegasus stands in the foreground, her wings raised and its gaze towards 
the sky.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
The artist portrays past and current Arcana members as mages and psionics
with an odd sense of humor and remarkably gaudy taste in clothing. You wonder
about the artist or perhaps the style in which this was painted - the way
that some of the figures are blurred and shimmering suggests that they were
phasing in and out of sight during the sitting.
*DESCRIPTION_END
