This landscape is faintly disturbing in its near-familiarity. You see tall 
crystal columns which seem to shift and distort under a crimson sky.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
A vase sits at the center of the table.
*DESCRIPTION_END
