  ECHO OTHERS %N pushes the clockwork model, making the planets and sun bob up and down.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH 7
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You push the model, sending Andor's moons to their complex dance of wax and wane.
  ECHO OTHERS %N pushes the model, sending Andor's moon spinning.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB BREAK 7
  CLEARVERB
  DAMAGEPLR BURN 6753 As you attempt to break the model, the tiny sun flares up, burning you!
  ECHO OTHERS As %N attemps to break the model, its tiny sun flares up, enveloping %i in flame!
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 7
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The model is a representation of Andor's solar system, complete with the planet's three moons.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TURN 7
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER As you turn the model, you notice how the sun revolves around Andor.
  ECHO OTHERS %N turns a clockwork model.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 4
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The bed is neatly made with prismatic gray sheets and a large pillow.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 0
  CLEARVERB
  SHOWROOM 251
  AFFECT 251
  ECHO ALL %N looks down from a window above.
  AFFECT 1674
ENDIF
;
; R# 498 : Guildmaster's Office
NUMBER 498
NAME Guildmaster's Office
ASTRAL
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This large office has a spectacular view of the western part of Fayd.
The floor is done in colored tiles creating two separate designs that
blend together in the center of the office, just in front of a large
teak desk. Diagrams and notes on the physics of the mind lay stacked
in neat and orderly piles upon the desk, while a comfortable chair
floats behind the desk.
*DESCRIPTION_END
; Door to landing 3.
ITEM 0 65 VAL1=200 VAL2=495 VAL3=1202
; Desk
ITEM 1 201 ADJ1=319
; Window
ITEM 2 249
; Old leather chair
ITEM 3 86 ADJ1=222 ADJ2=180
; Ucantsee
ITEM 9 693
;
IFPREVERB LOOK 2
  RANDOM dummy1 1 3 0
  IFVAR dummy1 = 1
    SHOWROOM 257
  ENDIF
  IFVAR dummy1 = 2
    SHOWROOM 255
  ENDIF
  IFVAR dummy1 = 3
    SHOWROOM 251
  ENDIF
ENDIF
;
; R# 1670 : Central Shaft, Sixth Floor
NUMBER 1670
NAME Central Shaft, Sixth Floor
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
A crystal pillar rises from the floor up into the center of the tower, 
surrounded by the floating blocks of a spiral staircase. An opening
that leads to a solarium.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT D 495
; Opening
ITEM 0 72 VAL2=1671
; crystal pillar
ITEM 4 1700 ADJ1=77
EXTEND 4 which is the center of a floating spiral staircase
; Ucantsee
ITEM 9 693
;
; R# 1671 : Arcana Tower, Solarium
NUMBER 1671
NAME Arcana Tower, Solarium
FOREST
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The solarium is surrounded by glass walls which allow light to shine in over
a garden composed of what must be every plant on Andor. Shay-am flowers,
nightshade and quillim trees as well as other, more traditional plants mix in
unnatural harmony with a few strange ones that are perhaps not native to
Andor. You shift your eyes away after they come to rest on a bush that seems
to be peering back at you. A path leads out to a patio.
*DESCRIPTION_END
; TREE DOOR WORK HERE??
; -Not unless you make the room Forest, I think.
; Opening
ITEM 0 72 VAL2=1670
; Path
ITEM 1 80 VAL2=1672
; Bush
ITEM 2 1232
; The bush here used to provide something for initiation, but I no longer see any reference
; to it in the script. Related to the lost portions of Brekken's Tower, probably.
; Wall
ITEM 3 420 ADJ1=143
; Tree
ITEM 4 229 ADJ1=327 ADJ2=577
; Ucantsee
ITEM 9 693
;
IFPREVERB LOOK 3
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER From this height you can see the entire city of Fayd and what lies beyond. The Eltinmar winds through grassy fields near Grymwood, while the Teeth of Shartan dominate the northern view.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 2
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER For a moment, you imagine that the bush is staring back at you, but you quickly dismiss the idea.
ENDIF
IFVERB SNIFF -1
  ECHO PLAYER One might expect the various fragrances to battle for dominance. Instead, they seem to blend together into a pleasantly spicy floral scent.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB MARK -1
  IFVAR INTNUM3 ! 1
    IFVAR ORG ! 2
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You feel dizzy.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
;
; R# 1672 : Tower Exterior, Patio
NUMBER 1672
NAME Tower Exterior, Patio
ASTRAL
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This small stone circle is positioned to catch the warmth of the sun during
the day and provide a good view of the stars and moon after dusk. Lounge
chairs cluster in a semi-circle around a small crystal fountain. A path leads
back inside.
*DESCRIPTION_END
; Fountain
ITEM 0 197 ADJ1=294 ADJ2=77
; Path
ITEM 1 80 VAL2=1671
; Water
ITEM 2 198 VAL2=300
; Chair
ITEM 3 86 ADJ2=1227
; Ucantsee
ITEM 9 693
;
ifpreverb concentrate -1
  ifvar intnum3 = 118
    skillcheck 26 -275 dummy1
    ifvar dummy1 >= 0
      clearverb
      echo player You feel yourself slip into another realm of being.
      echo others %N just seems to fade into obscurity.
      move 2226
      affect 2226
      echo others %N achieves this state of awareness.
    else
      clearverb
      echo player You concentrate and meditate.
      echo others %N concentrates.
      echo player [Round: 7 Sec]
      equal roundtime 7
    endif
  endif
ENDIF
IFPREVERB SIT -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You take a seat on one of the lounge chairs.
  ECHO OTHERS %N takes a seat on one of the lounge chairs.
  POSITION SIT
ENDIF
IFPREVERB STAND -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You stand up.
  ECHO OTHERS %N stands up.
  POSITION STAND
ENDIF
IFVERB LISTEN -1
  ECHO PLAYER The sounds of the city are distant, concealed by the musical tones coming from the fountain as the water falls into its basin.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB DRINK 2
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The water is cool and refreshing, with a faint unidentifiable aftertaste.
  ECHO OTHERS %N takes a drink from the fountain.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The fountain has been sculpted from a translucent crystal from the Deep Realms. Its basin produces gentle humming tones as water strikes it.
ENDIF
;
; R# 2502 : Silver Arcana, The Vault
NUMBER 2502
NAME Silver Arcana, The Vault
ASTRAL
DARKNESS
